#### Q40. Which is a valid CSS section for this XML code snippet?

```xml
<cars>
    <car><make>Cadillac</make><model>Escalade</model><year>2007</year></car>
    <car><make>Ford</make><model>Mustang</model><year>1968</year></car>
    <car><make>Mercedes</make><model>C-Class</model><year>1999</year></car>
</cars>
```

- %OPTION%

```css
cars {
  display: block;
}
car(make),
car(model),
car(year) {
  display: inline;
  padding-top: 0.5em;
}
```

- %OPTION%

```css
car, cars { display: block; }
make, model, year {
  display: inline;
  padding-top: 0.5em;
}
```

- %OPTION%

```css
cars {
  display: block;
}
car.make,
car.model,
car.year {
  display: inline;
  padding-top: 0.5em;
}
```

- %OPTION%

```css
cars {
  display: block;
}
car#make,
car#model,
car#year {
  display: inline;
  padding-top: 0.5em;
}
```
